Wendy Davis (actress) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wendy_Davis_(actress) 0 Wendy Davis (born June 30, 1966) is an American actress. She is best known for her role as Colonel Joan Burton in the Lifetime television drama series Army Wives (2007–2013), for which she received three NAACP Image Award for Outstanding Actress in a Drama Series nomination. In 2018, she began starring in the Oprah Winfrey Network comedy-drama series Love Is. Wendy_Davis ( born June_30_,_1966 ) is an_American_actress .
